@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! More than 12 inch deep water is staying put in almost every ground floor of the houses of Rajpur Sonarpur municipal area for at least 30 days a year for the last 5 yrs. For roads it's 20 inch &amp; 60 days respectively. Please do something.#Covid_19

@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! As per WB govt restrictions order on 15.9.21, all GOI offices of Kolkata/WB were supposed to bring roster order out on 15.9.21 itself. But, as on 27.9.21, there is no roster yet, in any Kol/WB GOI office. Compliance has to be enforced. #Covid_19
@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! I am Afraid that, after managing the first 2 waves of covid by showing most severely reduced no. Of deaths/infections (one- tenth of the real numbers), same is being done with vaccination albeit with much increased numbers this time. #Covid_19

@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! More than 12 inch deep water is staying put in almost every ground floor of the houses of Rajpur Sonarpur municipal area for at least 30 days a year for the last 5 yrs. For roads it's 20 inch &amp; 60 days respectively. Please do something.#Covid_19
@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! Water level during monsoon season in entire Rajpur Sonarpur municipality area is scaling new heights every year - for the last 5 years. I am a petty housewife, so I don't know the whys &amp; hows of it, but this is ground reality.#Covid_19

@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! More than 12 inch deep water is staying put in almost every ground floor of the houses of Rajpur Sonarpur municipal area for at least 30 days a year for the last 5 yrs. For roads it's 20 inch &amp; 60 days respectively. Please do something.#Covid_19
@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! Water level during monsoon season in entire Rajpur Sonarpur municipality area is scaling new heights every year - for the last 5 years. I am a petty housewife, so I don't know the whys &amp; hows of it, but this is ground reality.#Covid_19
@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! I beg to draw your kind attention to the fact that out of the last 100 days, 90% areas of Rajpur-Sonarpur municipality are under at least 18 inch deep water for at least 70 days now. I don't Know how &amp; why, but this is reality.#Covid_19

@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! 1 crore vaccination a day, 2 crore vaccination a day. India has seen it all ! BJP-GOI is even busy making God out of their leader. But still, only 13% Indians have completed 2 doses of vaccination. So, where are these doses going ! #Covid_19

@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! Every time, out of 14 days, all Kol/WB GOI offices are run with 100% staff sans roster for first 7 days. Then, for the rest, A roster comes out for the sake of it &amp; people are forced to keep 100% attendance. Compliance has to be enforced. #Covid_19
@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! More than 12 inch deep water is staying put in almost every ground floor of the houses of Rajpur Sonarpur municipal area for at least 30 days a year for the last 5 yrs. For roads it's 20 inch &amp; 60 days respectively. Please do something.#Covid_19
@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! Water level during monsoon season in entire Rajpur Sonarpur municipality area is scaling new heights every year - for the last 5 years. I am a petty housewife, so I don't know the whys &amp; hows of it, but this is ground reality.#Covid_19
@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! I beg to draw your kind attention to the fact that out of the last 100 days, 90% areas of Rajpur-Sonarpur municipality are under at least 18 inch deep water for at least 70 days now. I don't Know how &amp; why, but this is reality.#Covid_19

@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! Water level during monsoon season in entire Rajpur Sonarpur municipality area is scaling new heights every year - for the last 5 years. I am a petty housewife, so I don't know the whys &amp; hows of it, but this is ground reality.#Covid_19
@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! I beg to draw your kind attention to the fact that out of the last 100 days, 90% areas of Rajpur-Sonarpur municipality are under at least 18 inch deep water for at least 70 days now. I don't Know how &amp; why, but this is reality.#Covid_19

@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! As per WB govt restrictions order on 15.9.21, all GOI offices of Kolkata/WB were supposed to bring roster order out on 15.9.21 itself. But, as on 27.9.21, there is no roster yet, in any Kol/WB GOI office. Compliance has to be enforced. #Covid_19
@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! I am Afraid that, after managing the first 2 waves of covid by showing most severely reduced no. Of deaths/infections (one- tenth of the real numbers), same is being done with vaccination albeit with much increased numbers this time. #Covid_19

@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! More than 12 inch deep water is staying put in almost every ground floor of the houses of Rajpur Sonarpur municipal area for at least 30 days a year for the last 5 yrs. For roads it's 20 inch &amp; 60 days respectively. Please do something.#Covid_19
@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! Water level during monsoon season in entire Rajpur Sonarpur municipality area is scaling new heights every year - for the last 5 years. I am a petty housewife, so I don't know the whys &amp; hows of it, but this is ground reality.#Covid_19

@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! More than 12 inch deep water is staying put in almost every ground floor of the houses of Rajpur Sonarpur municipal area for at least 30 days a year for the last 5 yrs. For roads it's 20 inch &amp; 60 days respectively. Please do something.#Covid_19
@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! Water level during monsoon season in entire Rajpur Sonarpur municipality area is scaling new heights every year - for the last 5 years. I am a petty housewife, so I don't know the whys &amp; hows of it, but this is ground reality.#Covid_19
@MVenkaiahNaidu Respected Sir ! I beg to draw your kind attention to the fact that out of the last 100 days, 90% areas of Rajpur-Sonarpur municipality are under at least 18 inch deep water for at least 70 days now. I don't Know how &amp; why, but this is reality.#Covid_19
